title: 105: The Trader Joe’s Haul Episode: June ‘20 Edition!
itunes:title: The Trader Joe’s Haul Episode: June ‘20 Edition!
description: In this episode, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie are digging into some tasty finds from our favorite food trader! Finds like turkeyless turkey burgers, eggplant parm, black truffle ketchup, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, an amazing new hummus that you need to buy RIGHT NOW, and a new fruit spread that’s OUT OF THIS WORLD. So push play now, and when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of these finds!
itunes:summary: It’s been 3 months, but we’re back hauling, and what better place to start than Trader Joe’s?!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
